{"tid":225940,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"[你會點揀]代步車選擇","createTime":"2017-05-02T07:20:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-05T10:12:04.000Z","uid":33322,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ca27718d2c3c69730aae1f94cde0b597e0d936f4","tid":225940,"uid":33322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T07:20:25.000Z","msg":"最近諗住買架二手代步車揸下<br />\n主要係車父母，最多假日揸去郊區行山<br />\n唔好太貴～70000樓下，盡可能搵d 5－6年內既車<br />\n睇中左幾架，希望大家俾d意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\ncorolla － 安全，多氣袋，睇過d片應該都坐得舒適，不過size偏大架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\njazz － 公廁車，5－6年車個價應該會過7皮，放番出去都唔會蝕太多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n日產note － 細車仔但係後座幾多位，腳長少少都ok，不過放番出去應該唔值錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nmazda 3 － 個人覺得最靚仔，不過多電子野驚買左返黎多野執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nractis － 得2個氣袋，安全好似差少少，車身高舒服d <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：6尺1，屋企都偏高，米7米8"},{"pid":"9bc6dd20cafd55c8f2f0a15466ea1b0b4d3dafae","tid":225940,"uid":8963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T07:22:32.000Z","msg":"corolla 好細架喎巴打<br />\n如果依幾款車我會揀corolla 同Mazda 3"},{"pid":"f9cc7611392e286de76677aa8bcbcb9e9a6c5df8","tid":225940,"uid":5278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T07:23:33.000Z","msg":"jazz坐4個其實唔算逼"},{"pid":"679cc7d4c462c8fc48635419aacdd515606b5914","tid":225940,"uid":41394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T07:33:25.000Z","msg":"家庭車 車父母 唔要大架 不如諗下Honda Freed"},{"pid":"fd535cf0d9b5367db2879db5757f7c2d3b335745","tid":225940,"uid":33322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T07:44:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquot